injectables.name: ButtonService

components.name: ButtonComponent
IconComponent

modules.name: AppModule
ButtonModule

variables.name: azulButton
variables.defaultValue:
() => ({
  template:  `
    <ui-button 
      [text]="text" 
      [buttonType]="buttonType" 
      (onClick)="onClick($event)" 
      [disabled]= "disabled"
      [iconName] = "iconName"
      [iconSize] = "iconSize"></ui-button>`,
  props: {
    disabled : boolean('disabled', false),
    text : text('text', 'BUTTON'),
    iconName: text('Icon Name', 'edit'),
    iconSize: select(
      "Icon Size", 
      [16, 18, 24, 36, 48], 16),
    buttonType :  select(
    "Button type",
    ["neutral", "neutral-outline",  
      "sandstone", "sandstone-outline", 
      "classic", "classic-outline" , 
      "sunrise", "sunrise-outline",
      "carbon", "carbon-outline",
      "azul", "azul-outline",
      "warmgray", "warmgray-outline"],
    "azul"),
    onClick: () => action('Button clicked')('Click'),
  }
})
